---
title: Feta & Pesto Hasselback Chicken with Pear Salad & Spiced Potatoes
description: Can you get a more perfectly portioned plate? This nutritionally balanced meal has a healthy serve of chicken coated in the most delectable basil pesto, a crisp pear salad with loads of texture, and tasty roast potato chunks. Delish!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/fetta-pesto-hasselback-chicken-e09f2da0.jpg
